            </div>
          </li>

          <li>
            <button class="accordion btn-filter">When can I start&#63;</button>

            <div class="panel">
            <p>Once you accepted invitation by the advertiser and have sticker attached to your car&#44; you can start advertising.</p>
            </div>
          </li>

          <li>
            <button class="accordion btn-filter">How much money will I make&#63;</button>

            <div class="panel">
            <p>Qualified drivers earn &#36;500&#47;month for the duration of the campaign. All drivers have to do is drive as they normally would.
            However, it would also depends on the advertisers that you are matched with as well as the size &#38; type of advert applied to your car. </p>
            </div>
          </li>

          <li>
            <button class="accordion btn-filter">What are the decals made of&#63;</button>

            <div class="panel">
            <p>The decals are adhesive&#44; made of vinyl specifically used for cars. The vinyl will not damage your car &#45; it comes off very clean and actually protects your cars paint.</p>
            </div>
          </li>

          <li>
            <button class="accordion btn-filter">What parts of the car will be wrapped&#63;</button>

